Integration with Grok API for AI-driven commands and actions.
Responsive design using Tailwind CSS and Framer Motion.
Inherited Capabilities from CLI Version v1.0.5
Lightweight CLI assistant powered by Grok API from X.AI with vision support.
AI-powered agent with autonomous execution, agentic loop, and context-aware continuations.
Code operations: grep, read, edit, create files with security checks and glob patterns.
Task scheduling with cron jobs and automated commands.
Git integration: status, diff, log, add, commit, checkout, stash.
Skills system for installing and loading custom extensions from URLs.
Vision support for processing images through grok-vision-beta model.
Voice transcription from Telegram and Discord using OpenAI Whisper.
Web search and fetch capabilities.
Connectors for Telegram and Discord bots.
Custom Skills: openai-voice (voice capabilities), telegram.
Commands: /login, /logout, /config, /init, /grep, /files, /read, /write, /task, /skill, /usage, /context, /history, /clear, /help, and natural language queries.
Tech Stack: Bun runtime, TypeScript with strict mode, ESLint, Prettier, Biome for linting and formatting.
APIs and Integrations: X.AI Grok API (with vision), GitHub API for updates, Telegram, Discord, WhatsApp for notifications.
Architecture: Modular design with REPL loop, agentic loop for multi-step actions, security checks for destructive operations.
